# hcsr04 driver

This linux kernel driver of hcsr04 sensor uses the linux gpios core. 

Strongly inspired by my old version of this driver: driver_MIOgpio_PS.c. You can find it here: https://github.com/kuhiu/SmartNavSysAccelByHW.

